评论概述: Nice but a little too big beads...
评论详情: This style is all the rage this summer. And I got a set that had clasps but the "tails" of the chains were bugging me way too much. So I got the stretch version - much easier to wear. These are made well and should easily last through the summer. You never know with elastic when it's going to give up the ghost but they are easy to wear.  My other set has a more graduated set of beads. These seem to be two small bead bracelets, one medium bead bracelet, and two larger bead bracelets. If I were going to improve it - have five different sizes of beads graduating down.  But it's still a nice set and if you are sharing them with say a sister, this set would be very nice.  They aren't lose on my wrist - I have a 7" wrist - but they aren't tight enough to leave a dent unless I move them up my arm. So I try not to do that.  I do like the stacked bracelet look. If I was young and tan, they would probably look better! :D
